'''意大利足球甲级联赛最佳主教练'''（{{lang-it|Migliore allenatore AIC}}）是[[意大利足球运动员协会|意大利足球运动员协会]]颁发的年度奖项，奖励上一年[[意大利足球甲级联赛|意大利足球甲级联赛]]最突出的[[运动教练|教练]]，属[[意甲奥斯卡|意甲最佳]]系列奖项<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.repubblica.it/sport/calcio/2017/01/31/foto/gran_gala_del_calcio_tanti_premiati-157273798/1/#1 | work = [[共和國報|la Repubblica]] | title = Gran Galà del Calcio a Milano: gli juventini i più premiati | date = 2017-01-31 | accessdate = 2022-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200728032752/https://www.repubblica.it/sport/calcio/2017/01/31/foto/gran_gala_del_calcio_tanti_premiati-157273798/1/#1 | archive-date = 2020-07-28 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[尤文图斯足球俱乐部|尤文图斯]]是教练获奖最多的俱乐部，达11次；绝大部分得主是意大利人，只有两人例外，第一位是2000年的[[斯文·約蘭·艾歷臣|斯文·約蘭·艾歷臣]]，[[若泽·穆里尼奥|若泽·穆里尼奥]]则是首位两度获奖的外籍教练。[[马西米利亚诺·阿莱格里|马西米利亚诺·阿莱格里]]获奖次数最多，达四次。

== 历史 ==
[[1996年至1997年意大利足球甲级联赛|1996年至1997年意大利足球甲级联赛]]结束后，[[意甲奥斯卡|意甲奥斯卡]]将第一个意大利足球甲级联赛最佳主教练授予[[尤文图斯足球俱乐部|尤文图斯足球俱乐部]]教练[[马尔切洛·里皮|马尔切洛·里皮]]，球队在他引领下以超出[[帕爾馬足球會|帕爾馬足球會]]两分的优势夺冠<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital97.html | publisher = [[RSSSF|RSSSF.com]] | title = Italy Championship 1996/97 | date = 2000-01-31 | access-date = 2022-01-21 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-12-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211224234030/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital97.html }}</ref>；尤文图斯还在[[1996年欧洲冠军联赛决赛|1996年欧洲冠军联赛决赛]]战胜[[阿贾克斯足球俱乐部|阿贾克斯足球俱乐部]]<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/european/juventus-champions-league-final-ajax-doping-scandal-casts-dark-shadows-ahead-real-madrid-a7768061.html | work = The Independent | title = Juventus' controversial European past casts dark shadows ahead of Champions League final against Real Madrid | first = Jack | last = Pitt-Brooke | access-date = 2022-01-21 | date = 2017-06-01 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2020-11-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201122232036/https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/european/juventus-champions-league-final-ajax-doping-scandal-casts-dark-shadows-ahead-real-madrid-a7768061.html }}</ref>。[[1997年至1998年意大利足球甲级联赛|一年后]]尤文图斯连庄意甲，里皮再度获奖<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital98.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy Championship 1997/98 | date = 2017-04-27 | access-date = 2022-01-21 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-11-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211122154332/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital98.html }}</ref>，但球队在[[1997年欧洲冠军联赛决赛|欧冠决赛]]不敌“德意志常年弱者”[[多特蒙德足球俱樂部|多特蒙德足球俱樂部]]<ref>{{Cite web | dead-url = no | url = https://www.espn.co.uk/football/uefa-champions-league/2/blog/post/2313264/echoes-of-the-1997-champions-league-final-as-juventus-prepare-for-dortmund-clash | title = Echoes of the 1997 Champions League final as Juve prepare for Dortmund | publisher = ESPN | access-date = 2022-01-21 | first = Mina | last = Rzouki | date = 2015-02-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170921000252/http://www.espn.co.uk/football/uefa-champions-league/2/blog/post/2313264/echoes-of-the-1997-champions-league-final-as-juventus-prepare-for-dortmund-clash | archive-date = 2017-09-21 }}</ref>。[[阿爾貝托·扎凱羅尼|阿爾貝托·扎凱羅尼]]带领[[AC米兰|AC米兰]]赢得[[1998年至1999年意大利足球甲级联赛|1998至1999年联赛]]后获最佳主教练<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital99.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy Championship 1998/99 | date = 2001-07-09 | access-date = 2022-01-21 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211122233020/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital99.html | archive-date = 2021-11-22 }}</ref>。瑞典教练[[斯文·約蘭·艾歷臣|斯文·約蘭·艾歷臣]]引领[[拉素體育會|拉素體育會]]在[[1999年至2000年意大利足球甲级联赛|1999至2000年]]拿下1974年以来第一个联赛冠军，加上折桂[[1999年欧洲超级杯|欧洲超级杯]]和[[1999至2000年意大利杯|意大利杯]]，连串佳绩确保他当上首位外籍意甲最佳主教练<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.theguardian.com/football/these-football-times/2015/mar/30/sven-goran-eriksson-lazio-serie-a-1999-2000-mancini-milan | title = How Sven-Goran Eriksson's Lazio won the great Serie A title race of 1999–2000 | first = Blair | last = Newman | access-date = 2022-01-21 | date = 2015-03-30 | work = The Guardian | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220101181623/https://www.theguardian.com/football/these-football-times/2015/mar/30/sven-goran-eriksson-lazio-serie-a-1999-2000-mancini-milan | archive-date = 2022-01-01 }}</ref>。

尤文图斯在[[2000年至2001年意大利足球甲级联赛|2000至2001年联赛]]以两分之差落后[[羅馬體育俱樂部|羅馬體育俱樂部]]位居第二，但[[卡洛·安切洛蒂|卡洛·安切洛蒂]]入选最佳主教练，是首次主教练获奖但俱乐部未夺冠<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital01.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy Championship 2000/01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211104225746/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital01.html | archive-date = 2021-11-04 | date = 2005-09-01 | access-date = 2022-01-21 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[2001年至2002年意大利足球甲级联赛|第二年]]刚晋级的[[切沃维罗纳足球俱乐部|切沃维罗纳足球俱乐部]]拿到联赛第五的好成绩并取得[[2002–03年歐洲足協盃|2002–03年歐洲足協盃]]参赛资格，主教练[[路易吉·德尔内里|路易吉·德尔内里]]获奖<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital02.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy Championship 2001/02 | date = 2000-01-31 | access-date = 2022-01-21 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-03-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210307155423/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital02.html }}</ref><ref name="list">{{cite web | url = http://www.assocalciatori.it/Pagine/AlbodOro/tabid/161/language/en-US/Default.aspx | title = Albo d'Oro | publisher = assocalciatori.it | access-date = 2013-06-07 | archive-date = 2013-06-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130607005737/http://www.assocalciatori.it/Pagine/AlbodOro/tabid/161/language/en-US/Default.aspx | dead-url = yes}}</ref>。里皮带领尤文图斯赢得[[2002年至2003年意大利足球甲级联赛|2002至2003年意甲联赛]]，[[2002年意大利超级杯|意大利超级杯]]，球队还在[[2003年欧洲冠军联赛决赛|2003年欧洲冠军联赛决赛]]与同属意大利的帕尔玛队会师后以微弱优势胜出，随后他将最佳主教练获奖纪录提升到三次<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital03.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy Championship 2002/03 | date = 2000-01-31 | access-date = 2022-01-21 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211207092241/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital03.html | archive-date = 2021-12-07 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/news/0191-0e6a614266aa-896bd9663128-1000--all-italian-finals/ | publisher = UEFA | title = All-Italian finals | date = 2003-05-16 | access-date = 2022-01-21 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170920101753/http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/news/newsid%3D69576.html | archive-date = 2017-09-20 }}</ref>。AC米兰在[[2003年至2004年意大利足球甲级联赛|2003至2004年]]表现出众，以超出第二名罗马足球俱乐部11分的显著优势夺得五年来第一个联赛冠军<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital04.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy 2003/04 | date = 2005-08-19 | access-date = 2022-01-21 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211207092237/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital04.html | archive-date = 2021-12-07 }}</ref>，主教练安切洛蒂梅开二度<ref name="list" />。[[2004年至2005年意大利足球甲级联赛|第二年]][[法比奥·卡佩罗|法比奥·卡佩罗]]带领尤文图斯夺冠后拿下最佳主教练<ref>{{Cite web | access-date = 2022-01-21 | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital05.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy 2004/05 | date = 2000-01-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211207093155/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital05.html | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-12-07 }}</ref>，但在[[2006年意大利足球醜聞|2006年意大利足球醜聞]]爆发后辞职，尤文图斯降级[[意大利足球乙级联赛|意乙]]<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2017/05/03/juventus-went-back-became-european-heavyweights/ | title = How Juventus went to hell and back and became European heavyweights again | work = The Daily Telegraph | access-date = 2022-01-21 | date = 2017-05-03 | first = Charlie | last = Eccleshare | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210210000321/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2017/05/03/juventus-went-back-became-european-heavyweights/ | archive-date = 2021-02-10 }}</ref>。

罗马足球俱乐部教练[[卢西亚诺·斯帕莱蒂|卢西亚诺·斯帕莱蒂]]接下来连续两次获奖。球队在[[2005年至2006年意大利足球甲级联赛|2005至2006年联赛]]本只排第五，但丑闻令众多球队成绩取消，罗马队升至第二，在[[2005至2006年意大利杯|意大利杯]]同样位居第二，决赛时以一比四不敌[[国际米兰足球俱乐部|国际米兰足球俱乐部]]。<ref>{{Cite web | dead-url = no | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital06.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy 2005/06 | date = 2000-01-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211115064334/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital06.html | archive-date = 2021-11-15 | access-date = 2022-01-21 }}</ref>罗马在[[2006年至2007年意大利足球甲级联赛|2006至2007年联赛]]排第二并折桂[[2006至2007年意大利杯|意大利杯]]，斯帕莱蒂获颁最佳主教练<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital07.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy 2006/07 | date = 2000-01-31 | access-date = 2022-01-21 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220120095802/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital07.html | archive-date = 2022-01-21}}</ref>。[[佛罗伦萨足球俱乐部|佛罗伦萨足球俱乐部]]在[[2007年至2008年意大利足球甲级联赛|2007至2008年联赛]]排第四，还在[[2007–08年欧洲联盟杯|2007–08年欧洲联盟杯]]打进半决赛，主教练[[切薩雷·普蘭德利|切薩雷·普蘭德利]]2008年获奖<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital08.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy 2007/08 | date = 2000-01-31 | access-date = 2022-01-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220120025143/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital08.html | archive-date = 2022-01-20 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="list" />。

[[马西米利亚诺·阿莱格里|马西米利亚诺·阿莱格里]]在[[2010年至2011年意大利足球甲級聯賽|2010至2011年联赛]]接掌AC米兰<ref>{{cite news | title = The coach is Allegri! | url = http://www.acmilan.com/en/news/show/123982 | work = acmilan.com | publisher = [[AC米兰|Associazione Calcio Milan]] | access-date = 2016-03-03 | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303233909/http://www.acmilan.com/en/news/show/123982 | date = 2010-06-25 | archive-date = 2016-03-03}}</ref>，带领球队夺冠并打入[[2010年至2011年意大利杯|意大利杯]]半决赛，获意甲奥斯卡更名意甲最佳之际第一个最佳主教练奖<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital2011.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy 2010/11 | date = 2021-01-14 | access-date = 2022-01-21 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210302234111/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital2011.html | archive-date = 2021-03-02}}</ref>。下一位得主也是新教练，前球员[[安東尼奧·孔蒂|安東尼奧·孔蒂]][[2011年至2012年意大利足球甲級聯賽|2011至2012年联赛]]时接替德尔内里执掌尤文图斯，带领俱乐部赢得九年来第一个联赛冠军，同时打入[[2011年至2012年意大利杯|意大利杯]]决赛<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital2012.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy 2011/12 | date = 2021-01-14 | access-date = 2022-01-21 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-03-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210301002818/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital2012.html}}</ref>。孔蒂接下来两度连庄，尤文图斯[[2012年至2013年意大利足球甲級聯賽|2012至2013年联赛]]卫冕并折桂[[2012年意大利超级杯|意大利超级杯]]<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital2013.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy 2012/13 | date = 2021-01-14 | access-date = 2022-01-21 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-05-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210508000003/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital2013.html}}</ref>，[[2013年至2014年意大利足球甲级联赛|2013至2014年联赛]]达成三连冠<ref>{{Cite web | access-date = 2022-01-21 | dead-url = no | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital2014.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy 2013/14 | date = 2000-01-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210225100011/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital2014.html | archive-date = 2021-02-25}}</ref>。接下来孔蒂前去执掌[[意大利國家足球隊|意大利国家队]]，阿莱格里接手尤文图斯后也连续两次获封最佳主教练。球队[[2014年至2015年意大利足球甲級聯賽|联赛卫冕]]并夺得[[2014至2015年意大利杯|意大利杯]]，[[2014年意大利超级杯|意大利超级杯]]和[[2014–15年歐洲冠軍聯賽|欧冠联赛]]均排第二。<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2014/07/16/sport/football/football-allegri-conte-juventus/index.html | title = Massimiliano Allegri succeeds Antonio Conte as Juventus coach | publisher = CNN | date = 2014-07-16 | access-date = 2022-01-21 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210421214640/http://edition.cnn.com/2014/07/16/sport/football/football-allegri-conte-juventus/index.html | archive-date = 2021-04-21}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital2015.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy 2014/15 | date = 2000-01-31 | access-date = 2022-01-21 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200224012833/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital2015.html | archive-date = 2020-02-24}}</ref>阿莱格里带领尤文图斯在[[2015年至2016年意大利足球甲级联赛|2015至2016年联赛]]实现五连冠，卫冕[[2015年意大利超级杯|意大利超级杯]]和[[2015至2016年意大利杯|意大利杯]]<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital2016.html | publisher = RSSSF.com | title = Italy 2015/16 | date = 2000-01-31 | access-date = 2022-01-21 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210629012302/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ital2016.html | archive-date = 2021-06-29}}</ref>。

[[莫里斯奧·沙利|莫里斯奧·沙利]]带领[[那不勒斯足球俱乐部|那不勒斯足球俱乐部]]在[[2016年至2017年意大利足球甲级联赛|2016至2017年联赛]]夺得第三名，以83分创下球队新纪录，进球数位居联赛榜首<ref>{{Cite web | date = 2017-05-20 | title = Napoli, record di punti in Serie A | archive-date = 2019-03-08 | access-date = 2022-01-21 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190308054203/http://www.corrieredellosport.it/news/calcio/serie-a/napoli/2017/05/20-26040578/napoli_record_di_punti_in_serie_a/ | website = Corriere dello Sport | url = https://www.corrieredellosport.it/news/calcio/serie-a/napoli/2017/05/20-26040578/napoli_record_di_punti_in_serie_a}}</ref>，为他赢得最佳主教练奖。接下来阿莱格里第四次带领尤文图斯实现[[2017年至2018年意大利足球甲级联赛|联赛]]与意大利杯双冠王，把最佳主教练获奖纪录提升到四次<ref>{{Cite web | title = Allegri named best manager in Italy for the fourth time! - Juventus | url = https://www.juventus.com/en/news/articles/allegri-named-best-manager-in-italy-for-the-fourth-time | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210610002600/https://www.juventus.com/en/news/articles/allegri-named-best-manager-in-italy-for-the-fourth-time | archive-date = 2021-06-10 | access-date = 2022-01-21 | website = Juventus.com}}</ref>。[[2018年至2019年意大利足球甲级联赛|2018至2019年联赛]]期间，[[基恩·派路·加斯柏連尼|基恩·派路·加斯柏連尼]]带领[[阿特蘭大貝加莫足球會|阿特蘭大貝加莫足球會]]在23年来首度打入[[2018至2019年意大利杯|意大利杯]]决赛，成为又一位球队未能夺冠的最佳主教练<ref>{{Cite web | last = Longhi | first = Guglielmo | date = 2019-04-25 | title = Atalanta-Fiorentina 2-1: Ilicic-Gomez, Gasp in finale. Muriel non basta ai viola | archive-date = 2020-11-07 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.gazzetta.it/Calcio/Coppa-Italia/25-04-2019/atalanta-fiorentina-2-1-ilicic-gomez-gasp-finale-muriel-non-basta-viola-3301060046824.shtml | access-date = 2022-01-21 | website = La Gazzetta dello Sport | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201107233917/https://www.gazzetta.it/Calcio/Coppa-Italia/25-04-2019/atalanta-fiorentina-2-1-ilicic-gomez-gasp-finale-muriel-non-basta-viola-3301060046824.shtml}}</ref>，球队最后不敌拉齐奥，但又取得史上首次[[2019–20年歐洲冠軍聯賽|欧冠联赛]]资格<ref>{{Cite web | last = Sala | first = Federico | dead-url = no | date = 2019-05-26 | title = Atalanta-Sassuolo 3-1: i bergamaschi fanno la storia, è Champions League | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200916185703/https://www.repubblica.it/sport/calcio/serie-a/2019/05/26/news/atalanta-sassuolo_3-1_i_bergamaschi_fanno_la_storia_e_champions_league-227264452/ | access-date = 2022-01-21 | url = https://www.repubblica.it/sport/calcio/serie-a/2019/05/26/news/atalanta-sassuolo_3-1_i_bergamaschi_fanno_la_storia_e_champions_league-227264452/ | website = la Repubblica | archive-date = 2020-09-16}}</ref>。亚特兰大[[2019年至2020年意大利足球甲级联赛|第二年]]实现俱乐部意甲史上最高分（78分），加斯柏連尼再获最佳主教练<ref name="gasp2">{{Cite web | url = https://www.football-italia.net/167974/gran-gal%C3%A0-del-calcio-winners | title = Gran Galà del Calcio: The winners | date = 2021-03-19 | publisher = Football Italia | access-date = 2021-05-16 | archive-date = 2021-05-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210516065055/https://www.football-italia.net/167974/gran-gal%C3%A0-del-calcio-winners | dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | date = 2020-08-04 | title = 5 domande sull'Atalanta dei record | url = https://www.atalanta.it/news/5-domande-sullatalanta-dei-record/ | access-date = 2022-01-21 | website = Atalanta.it | archive-date = 2022-01-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220121164509/https://www.atalanta.it/news/5-domande-sullatalanta-dei-record/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

